text.section:
"License" means:
a license issued by the Comptroller under § 16-205(a) of this subtitle to:
act as a manufacturer;
act as a subwholesaler;
act as a vending machine operator;
act as a wholesaler; or
act as a storage warehouse; or
a license issued by the clerk under § 16-205(b) of this subtitle to act as a retailer.
